## plugin name - specifies name of shared library to be loaded relative to
## CHANGE: DELETED. hide it from sysadmin. make the plugin loading/configuration automatic. if a gridftpd/filedir block is enabled, load the right plugin automatically.

## allowaccess authgroup [authgroup ...] - (previously groupcfg) Specifies authorization groups
